    - Informations

    * Name:             Pyabr
    * Founder:          Mani Jamali
    * Developers:       PyFarsi Community
    * Package Manager:  Paye, PyPI
    * License:          GNU General Publice License v3.0

    - Official Website

    * Persian Page:     https://pyabr.ir
    * English Page:     https://en.pyabr.ir

    - Package Manager

    * Install:          `sudo paye in [package-name]`   e.g.: `sudo paye in ir.pyabr`
    * Remove:           `sudo paye rm [package-name]`
    * Update Repo:      `sudo paye in ir.pyabr.updates`
    * Update:           `sudo paye up`